is, is goodthe very best. Tom, thereour cook, sir
he will make the very best of itbroils ham the
best of any negro in the southern country, and his
hoecake
,
sir, is absolutely perfection. He does turn a
griddle with a dexterity that is remarkable. But you
shall seeyou shall see for yourself. Here, Tom!
And rolling up his sleeves, he took the subject of
