Standturnbrave menmen of Virginia! I come
to lead you back. Turn, cowardsfor your country
for yourselves! Shame me notshame me not; but
rally. Come with me; lookI myself will lead you!
But they heardthey heeded nothing of his
exhortations
.
He threw himself directly in front of the
fugitives, and with drawn sword, striking around him,
as if among his enemies, he vainly endeavoured to
compel
