if you please. He, only, will attend me.'
Proctor bowed, and departed.
Fatheroh! my fatherit is not the hourit is
not time yetdo not gonot yet! Robert may not be
readynot quite ready. He has to come from the
Cypress
he
has a great deal to do, and will want all the
